# Bazel configuration for dsp-api.
#
# Scope today: the `knora-sipi` OCI image build (rules_oci). The Scala build
# stays on sbt — see build.sbt and the Makefile docker-* targets. Image tags
# are passed explicitly by the Makefile, so no workspace-status stamping here.

common --incompatible_disallow_empty_glob
build --show_timestamps
